19
20class ByteArray;
21
22namespace DataMatrix {
23
24class SymbolInfo;
25
26/**
27* Error Correction Code for ECC200.
28*/
29class ECEncoder
30{
31public:
32 /**
33 * Creates the ECC200 error correction for an encoded message.
34 *
35 * @param codewords the codewords
36 * @param symbolInfo information about the symbol to be encoded
37 * @return the codewords with interleaved error correction.
38 */
39 static void EncodeECC200(ByteArray& codewords, const SymbolInfo& symbolInfo);
40};
